Description: GTK4 helper for the Internet Archive
 IA Helper simplifies searching for and downloading items, collections,
 and lists from the Internet Archive (archive.org), operating within the
 Archive's usage guidelines: it identifies itself, limits concurrent
 connections, verifies downloads against published checksums, and honors
 access restrictions on lending-library material.
